parameter 2: In the DVD version and syndicated reruns, the song that played during the cold opening scene in the original 1989 airing has been replaced. This is evident as the new song's lyrics reference 'Andy Garcia (I)' (qv)'s role in _Godfather: Part III, The (1990)_ (qv), 'Lisa 'Left Eye' Lopes' (qv)'s arson incident which did not occur until 1994 and the group 'Kris Kross' (qv) who did not debut until 1992.
parameter 3: The premieres of season 2 and 3 originally aired commercial-free and were about 52 minutes long. There are also 44 minute versions for syndication that have had several scenes edited out.
